{DIALOGUE}: And a couple of half gallons of milk.
{DIALOGUE}: And some soup.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He goes over to the fridge and puts two half gallons of milk in the bag.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Some soup.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Costello turns to Colin.
