{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. A STREET IN BOSTON. DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A BLACK-WINDOWED, MODERN, POLICE BUILDING, beetling over a plaza.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Older Boston reflected in the featureless glass.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Boston of this film is almost futuristic.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: COLIN looks up at the building with great intensity.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He puts on his sunglasses and walks towards the door.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. QUEENAN'S OFFICE. DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: COLIN, in civvies (a very good suit), stands at suave attention before CAPTAIN QUEENAN, a mild and scholarly man who might as well be a Jesuit history-teacher.
