{DIALOGUE}: You got any suits at home or you like coming to work looking like you're gonna invade Poland.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. QUEENAN'S OFFICE. DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BILLY is still at attention.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DIGNAM going with wet thumb through papers.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SGT. DIGNAM
