{DIALOGUE}: I got kicked out about four months ago.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SEAN
{DIALOGUE}: It was in the papers.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sean is a villain leaning in a doorway.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bad tie: he takes it off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He has been at a funeral.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: Well.
{DIALOGUE}: So you know.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SEAN
{DIALOGUE}: And why are we graced with your presence?
