{DIALOGUE}: As a matter of fact I have never had ten thousand dollars.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: That's what I'm saying.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sean nods, and nods.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SEAN
{DIALOGUE}: You know what we usually say at these moments.
{META_DATA}: (CONTINUED)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 29.
{META_DATA}: CONTINUED:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: You fuckin' moron.
