{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. A HOUSING PROJECT IN SOUTHIE. DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: COLIN and BARRIGAN (who Colin has moved to plain clothes) stand at the door, talking, or trying to talk, with a fearful MRS KENNEFICK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: MRS KENNEFICK looks like she starts drinking whiskey at 9 in the morning.
