{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. STREET NEAR TARGET BUILDING - NIGHT 103A
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A few blocks from the target building, a Police Tactical unit stops the departing Triad cars with a roadblock.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As officers approach the cars they realize they are empty except for hired Caucasian drivers.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An officer reports this to the command center.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. COLIN'S APARTMENT. DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Colin is asleep on the couch, in a bachelor disaster of Chinese food boxes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Something on TV: "Audition."
