{DIALOGUE}: Fuck you.
{META_DATA}: (safeties the gun)
{DIALOGUE}: I'm arresting you.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COLIN
{DIALOGUE}: That's the stupidest thing you could do.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: Shut up, shut up, shut the fuck up.
{META_DATA}: (hits him)
{DIALOGUE}: I don't give a fuck if these charges don't stick.
{META_DATA}: (whaling him in the beats)
{DIALOGUE}: But I'm still fucking arresting you.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: COLIN is hammered to his knees.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Head down, blood in his hair, drooling blood, thinking (impossibly) about his next move.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He seems to realize he's fucked.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: [You are what you do.]
{DIALOGUE}: Get up.
{META_DATA}: (COLIN doesn't move.)
{DIALOGUE}: I said get the fuck up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BILLY grabs the back of Colin's collar and puts the gun to Colin's head.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A crunch of gravel, off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BILLY and COLIN both hear it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BROWN
{DIALOGUE}: Put down the weapon and step away from Sergeant Sullivan.
