{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Brown is aiming his weapon.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: I called you.
{DIALOGUE}: You specifically.
{DIALOGUE}: You know who I am.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm not gonna shoot.
