{DIALOGUE}: Help me.
{META_DATA}: (CONTINUED)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 149.
{META_DATA}: CONTINUED: (3)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy realizes he's in a truly shitty situation: appearances are everything.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BROWN
{DIALOGUE}: Put the weapon on the deck and step away from Sergeant Sullivan.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COLIN
{META_DATA}: (a mess, bloody-mouthed)
